To create new user key
-----------------------
openssl genrsa-out mukesh.key 2048

Create new user certificate
----------------------------
openssl req -new -key mukesh.key -subj "/CN=mukesh" -out mukesh.csr

Create certificate signing request (CSR) for approval or signing of certificate by CA.

--------------------------

apiVersion: certificates.k8s.io/v1beta1
kind: CertificateSigningRequest
metadata:
  name: mukesh
spec:
  signerName: kubernetes.io/kube-apiserver-client
  groups:
  - system:authenticated
